title: Ms. Deanna Durbin - old-fashioned  appeal (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Here are some nice old fashioned style singing renditions from Canadian born
California raised Ms. Deanna Durbin. We include a "converted from DVD" version
of "Gimme a little kiss" at a nice bitrate too.


Why dont folks sound like this anymore huh! It was certainly more sanely
romantic - than rap music now heard around our gals, in any event!


Michael Rizzo Chessman
